WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:07.400
Jennifer Lopez, by Rod Smith. Penguin Readers, Level

00:07.400 --> 00:15.940
1. Jennifer Lopez. She can dance. She

00:15.940 --> 00:19.800
can sing. She is a smart business woman.

00:20.940 --> 00:25.940
She is beautiful and she is Hollywood's number

00:25.940 --> 00:31.860
1 Latina Movie Star. But the story of

00:31.860 --> 00:39.060
Jennifer Lopez starts in New York. Young Jennifer.

00:40.560 --> 00:41.540
It

00:41.540 --> 00:47.800
is July 24, 1970. A hot summer day

00:47.800 --> 00:52.480
in the Bronx, New York. A lot of

00:52.480 --> 00:54.480
Puerto Rican people live

00:54.480 --> 00:59.940
here and they are not all happy. But

00:59.940 --> 01:02.780
it is a good day for David and

01:02.780 --> 01:05.240
Guadalupe Lopez and their

01:05.240 --> 01:11.060
daughters Linda and Leslie. They are happy because

01:11.060 --> 01:13.320
they have a new little girl in the

01:13.320 --> 01:24.460
family. They

01:24.460 --> 01:28.540
hold. She performs for the family. Sometimes she

01:28.540 --> 01:32.680
is a singer. Sometimes she is a dancer

01:32.680 --> 01:33.960
or a movie

01:33.960 --> 01:39.060
star. She loves the movie West Side Story.

01:39.940 --> 01:45.580
She watches it 100 times. In West Side

01:45.580 --> 01:46.080
Story,

01:46.080 --> 01:52.760
Rita Moreno plays Anita. For Jennifer, Rita is

01:52.760 --> 01:58.380
America's number 1 actress and dancer. I'd like

01:58.380 --> 01:58.800
to be

01:58.800 --> 02:05.980
her, Jennifer thinks. At 5, Jennifer goes to

02:05.980 --> 02:10.140
a school of theater and dance. In a

02:10.140 --> 02:10.880
short time,

02:10.880 --> 02:15.240
she can sing, act and dance very well.

02:17.280 --> 02:21.600
But is this important? David and Guadalupe ask.

02:23.200 --> 02:23.680
They have

02:23.680 --> 02:27.240
good jobs. They want to see Jennifer in

02:27.240 --> 02:31.900
a good job too. For this, schoolwork is

02:31.900 --> 02:32.840
very important.

02:35.860 --> 02:42.500
Jennifer the dancer. In 1975, Jennifer goes to

02:42.500 --> 02:45.800
the Holy Family Catholic School in New York.

02:46.620 --> 02:47.180
It is a

02:47.180 --> 02:50.260
good school and she is a good student.

02:51.500 --> 02:58.560
But in 1983, the problems start. Now, schoolwork

02:58.560 --> 02:59.460
is not very

02:59.460 --> 03:03.320
important to Jennifer. She wants to be a

03:03.320 --> 03:11.060
performer. One day, in 1988, she says, I

03:11.060 --> 03:12.280
want to stop going to

03:12.280 --> 03:18.840
school. David and Guadalupe are angry. Jennifer is

03:18.840 --> 03:22.880
angry with them too. She walks out of

03:22.880 --> 03:23.380
the house.

03:24.920 --> 03:27.800
Jennifer lives in her dance school for a

03:27.800 --> 03:31.720
short time. Then she moves into an apartment

03:31.720 --> 03:32.580
in Manhattan

03:32.580 --> 03:37.040
with some friends. She dances in the school

03:37.040 --> 03:42.820
every day. She works well. Then, she starts

03:42.820 --> 03:53.360
to look for a

03:53.360 --> 03:56.780
first. She gets a job in the theater

03:56.780 --> 04:01.900
show Golden Musicals of Broadway. The show goes

04:01.900 --> 04:02.480
to Europe.

04:04.000 --> 04:08.080
Then, after five months, she gets a job

04:08.080 --> 04:12.900
in a new show, Synchronicity. This show goes

04:12.900 --> 04:13.500
to Japan.

04:13.500 --> 04:19.940
In 1991, Jennifer is back in the U

04:19.940 --> 04:23.720
.S. She is a very good dancer now

04:23.720 --> 04:26.180
and she is beautiful too.

04:27.580 --> 04:30.260
A lot of famous singers want the young

04:30.260 --> 04:35.560
dancer for their short music movies. Jennifer dances

04:35.560 --> 04:36.680
behind the

04:36.680 --> 04:42.580
singer Janet Jackson. This helps her and she

04:42.580 --> 04:45.480
meets important people in the movie business.

04:47.480 --> 04:49.860
There are no problems with her family now.

04:50.940 --> 04:53.680
She has work and she is a success.

04:55.120 --> 04:56.800
She has a boyfriend too,

04:57.620 --> 05:03.520
David Cruz. Later that year, Jennifer moves to

05:03.520 --> 05:06.480
Los Angeles for the famous TV show

05:06.680 --> 05:11.000
In Living Color. Jennifer is a dancer in

05:11.000 --> 05:13.580
the show but she is not always happy

05:13.580 --> 05:14.360
in her job.

05:15.620 --> 05:18.040
She wants to be an actress.

05:21.020 --> 05:25.840
Jennifer the actress. The head of the TV

05:25.840 --> 05:29.260
show South Central likes Jennifer's work.

05:30.010 --> 05:34.240
In 1993, he wants an actress for the

05:34.240 --> 05:39.820
show. He gives the job to Jennifer. After

05:39.820 --> 05:40.800
South Central,

05:41.220 --> 05:46.120
Jennifer works in three new TV shows. Second

05:46.120 --> 05:51.360
Chances, Malibu Road, and Nurses on the Line,

05:51.590 --> 05:56.800
The Crash of Flight 7. Jennifer is now

05:56.800 --> 05:58.520
a famous TV star.

06:00.070 --> 06:05.340
Then, in 1995, she is in her first

06:05.340 --> 06:08.960
Hollywood movie Me Familia.

06:10.290 --> 06:15.240
Me Familia is a Latin movie. Her first

06:15.240 --> 06:19.880
English movies are Money Train and Jack.

06:21.360 --> 06:26.840
In Money Train, Jennifer is Grace Santiago, a

06:26.840 --> 06:28.300
New York police woman.

06:29.220 --> 06:33.180
Wesley Snipes and Woody Harrelson play two brothers.

06:34.160 --> 06:35.780
They work for the police too.

06:36.900 --> 06:41.200
The two men love Grace. The movie is

06:41.200 --> 06:42.100
about their problems.

06:44.240 --> 06:48.560
Jack is a funny movie. Robin Williams plays

06:48.560 --> 06:49.860
a boy, Jack.

06:50.660 --> 06:54.120
People look at Jack and think, he's not

06:54.120 --> 06:58.540
a boy, he's a man. Jennifer plays Jack's

06:58.540 --> 06:59.120
teacher.

07:01.140 --> 07:04.440
In her movies, Jennifer is in love stories

07:04.440 --> 07:09.540
with famous men. Her boyfriend, David, is unhappy

07:09.540 --> 07:10.020
about

07:10.020 --> 07:12.980
this, and he goes back to New York.

07:14.640 --> 07:19.260
Jennifer is unhappy too. But then, she finds

07:19.260 --> 07:20.000
a new boyfriend.

07:21.260 --> 07:24.540
His name is Ohane Noah, and he is

07:24.540 --> 07:29.060
from Cuba. She marries him in 1997.

07:31.160 --> 07:34.520
In the same year, Jennifer is in four

07:34.520 --> 07:39.100
movies. The first movie is Blood and Wine,

07:39.400 --> 07:44.240
with two very famous actors, Jack Nicholson and

07:44.240 --> 07:48.880
Michael Caine. The movie is about two bad

07:48.880 --> 07:49.340
men,

07:50.220 --> 07:56.700
Alex Gates and Victor Spansky. Jennifer is Gabriella,

07:57.320 --> 07:58.380
Alex's girlfriend.

08:00.300 --> 08:04.060
After Blood and Wine, Jennifer is in the

08:04.060 --> 08:10.440
movies Anaconda, U-turn and Selena. The movies

08:10.440 --> 08:10.820
are a

08:10.820 --> 08:14.440
success in the U.S. but Selena is

08:14.440 --> 08:18.820
a success in Latin countries too. In Selena,

08:19.240 --> 08:20.400
Jennifer plays

08:20.960 --> 08:27.160
Selena Quinta Nia, the famous Mexican singer. It

08:27.160 --> 08:30.360
is an unhappy story because the singer's life

08:30.360 --> 08:35.140
was very short. Selena's father gives money for

08:35.140 --> 08:39.640
the movie. The director is Gregory Nava.

08:40.900 --> 08:43.840
Jennifer works on the movie in front of

08:43.840 --> 08:48.840
Selena's family. This is difficult, but the family

08:48.840 --> 08:49.260
likes

08:49.260 --> 08:53.020
Jennifer, and the movie teaches people about their

08:53.020 --> 08:56.160
daughter. This makes Jennifer happy

08:56.820 --> 09:01.760
because she liked Selena. Selena is a big

09:01.760 --> 09:05.160
success in many countries. Suddenly,

09:05.700 --> 09:09.140
Jennifer Lopez is not only a famous name

09:09.140 --> 09:10.080
in the U.S.

09:11.400 --> 09:18.140
The year 1998 arrives. Jennifer is happy, but

09:18.140 --> 09:21.680
she can't take a vacation. She is in

09:21.680 --> 09:22.360
two movies

09:22.360 --> 09:28.060
that year, Out of Sight and Ants. In

09:28.060 --> 09:32.420
Out of Sight, Jennifer is Karen Sisko, a

09:32.420 --> 09:33.200
police woman.

09:33.940 --> 09:39.260
George Clooney is Jack Foley. Foley takes money

09:39.260 --> 09:42.100
from a bank. He gets away from the

09:42.100 --> 09:42.540
police

09:43.180 --> 09:47.160
and takes Karen with him. The story is

09:47.160 --> 09:51.580
about their love. Ants is a movie for

09:51.580 --> 09:51.960
children.

09:53.040 --> 09:56.040
We hear Jennifer, but we don't see her

09:56.040 --> 09:56.400
face.

09:59.340 --> 10:00.900
Men and Movies

10:02.560 --> 10:08.580
Jennifer's 1998 movies are a big success, but

10:08.580 --> 10:13.540
O'Hane isn't happy. He and David have

10:13.540 --> 10:14.780
the same problem.

10:16.100 --> 10:18.880
They don't like to see Jennifer with men

10:18.880 --> 10:23.180
in love stories. O'Hane moves away.

10:24.140 --> 10:29.720
Later, he and Jennifer divorce, but they meet

10:29.720 --> 10:31.800
often and they are good friends.

10:33.100 --> 10:38.980
In 1999, Jennifer has a new boyfriend. His

10:38.980 --> 10:42.580
name is Sean Coombs. He is a famous

10:42.580 --> 10:43.460
black singer.

10:45.300 --> 10:51.940
On December 27, 1999, Sean and Jennifer come

10:51.940 --> 10:54.440
out of a dance bar and get in

10:54.440 --> 10:55.040
their car.

10:56.540 --> 11:00.560
The police stop them. They find a gun

11:00.560 --> 11:04.040
in the front of the car. The gun

11:04.040 --> 11:05.480
is not Sean's,

11:05.480 --> 11:10.420
but the police take him away. Jennifer is

11:10.420 --> 11:13.180
in the back of the car. It is

11:13.180 --> 11:14.300
not her problem.

11:15.640 --> 11:20.760
The story is in the newspapers. Early in

11:20.760 --> 11:24.080
2000, Jennifer stops seeing Sean.

11:24.080 --> 11:28.560
In that year, she makes the movie The

11:28.560 --> 11:33.540
Cell. Jennifer plays Catherine Dean, a doctor.

11:35.360 --> 11:39.420
Vincent D'Onofrio plays Carl, a bad man.

11:40.800 --> 11:44.000
He takes a young girl, but where is

11:44.000 --> 11:44.300
she?

11:44.300 --> 11:52.020
In 2001, Jennifer stars in The Wedding Planner.

11:52.980 --> 11:55.600
This is a funny movie and a love

11:55.600 --> 11:56.100
story.

11:57.700 --> 12:03.460
Jennifer plays Maria Fiore. Maria falls in love

12:03.460 --> 12:06.080
with Steve Edison, a doctor.

12:07.040 --> 12:10.600
The Wedding Planner is the number one movie

12:10.600 --> 12:17.160
of 2001. In the same year, Jennifer marries

12:17.160 --> 12:18.100
Chris Judd,

12:18.680 --> 12:23.400
a dancer, but they divorce in August 2002.

12:25.940 --> 12:30.120
Jennifer stars in Two Thrillers, Angel Eyes,

12:30.680 --> 12:35.680
and Enough. Then she is in Made in

12:35.680 --> 12:37.820
Manhattan, a love story.

12:40.220 --> 12:43.060
Jennifer starts going out with the actor Ben

12:43.060 --> 12:48.420
Affleck. In 2003, they star in the movie

12:48.420 --> 12:49.640
Glee.

12:50.780 --> 12:53.640
A lot of newspapers don't like the movie,

12:54.160 --> 12:55.960
but Glee makes money.

12:57.660 --> 13:01.880
Are Ben and Jennifer going to marry? People

13:01.880 --> 13:07.520
ask. The answer is no. Jennifer's love story

13:07.520 --> 13:08.920
finishes in September.

13:10.540 --> 13:15.040
But in 2004, Ben and Jennifer act in

13:15.040 --> 13:18.720
Jersey Girl, the story of a father and

13:18.720 --> 13:19.500
his little girl.

13:20.140 --> 13:23.080
Jennifer is not the star of that movie.

13:24.880 --> 13:28.920
After Jersey Girl comes Shall We Dance with

13:28.920 --> 13:29.780
Richard Geer.

13:30.760 --> 13:32.860
It is a love story about a dance

13:32.860 --> 13:37.440
teacher and her student. Jennifer sings for it

13:37.440 --> 13:38.460
with her friend,

13:38.920 --> 13:43.860
Mark Anthony. Some people are unhappy about Jennifer's

13:43.860 --> 13:48.320
movies at this time. Jennifer doesn't act well,

13:48.320 --> 13:53.380
and the stories aren't interesting, they say. But

13:53.380 --> 13:56.600
2004 is a good year for Jennifer.

13:57.800 --> 14:02.620
She falls in love with Mark. Jennifer and

14:02.620 --> 14:05.200
Mark marry, and they are very happy.

14:06.360 --> 14:10.140
After the movie's Monster in Law, An Unfinished

14:10.140 --> 14:12.220
Life, and Border Town,

14:13.140 --> 14:19.100
Jennifer and Mark star in El Cantante. Mark

14:19.100 --> 14:22.840
plays the famous Puerto Rican singer, Hector Lavo.

14:23.660 --> 14:31.740
Lavo married Pucci, and Jennifer plays her. Jennifer

14:31.740 --> 14:36.040
the singer. Music was always important to

14:36.040 --> 14:40.800
Jennifer. Today, the famous actress is a famous

14:40.800 --> 14:47.200
singer too. Jennifer's music success story starts

14:47.200 --> 14:53.340
in 1999. In that year, she makes On

14:53.340 --> 14:56.680
The Six. It is her first music CD.

14:57.600 --> 15:05.640
The name comes from the

15:05.640 --> 15:09.380
station near her home in New York. On

15:09.380 --> 15:14.220
the CD, she sings No Meyames with Mark

15:14.220 --> 15:14.740
Anthony.

15:15.940 --> 15:19.140
She sings in English too, but the music

15:19.140 --> 15:24.220
is Latin. After only five weeks, if you

15:24.220 --> 15:25.200
had my love,

15:25.620 --> 15:29.360
from the same CD is number one in

15:29.360 --> 15:33.520
the US. The success of Jennifer the singer

15:33.520 --> 15:35.020
doesn't stop.

15:35.820 --> 15:41.600
In 2001, her CD JLo is again number

15:41.600 --> 15:45.020
one in the US. She is the first

15:45.020 --> 15:47.400
singer actress with a CD

15:47.960 --> 15:51.880
and a movie, The Wedding Planner, at number

15:51.880 --> 15:54.100
one in the same week.

15:55.800 --> 16:02.840
In 2002, Jennifer makes two music CDs. The

16:02.840 --> 16:06.580
first CD of that year is J to

16:06.580 --> 16:09.020
the L.O. the remixes.

16:09.840 --> 16:13.760
It gets to number one too. After that,

16:14.540 --> 16:18.660
this is me then gets to number two.

16:20.460 --> 16:27.840
Jennifer's CD Rebirth arrives in 2005. It gets

16:27.840 --> 16:31.800
to number two in the US. Then Jennifer

16:31.800 --> 16:32.540
makes her

16:32.540 --> 16:40.120
CD. It is in Spanish. A lot of

16:40.120 --> 16:43.540
Latin people love this CD and it is

16:43.540 --> 16:45.300
number one in Mexico.

16:47.280 --> 16:55.840
In September 2007, Jennifer's CD Brave arrives. It

16:55.840 --> 16:59.300
doesn't have the same success and only gets

16:59.300 --> 17:01.920
to number 12 in the US.

17:05.560 --> 17:10.760
Success in Business Jennifer Lopez is not only

17:10.760 --> 17:14.100
an actress. She is not only a dancer

17:14.700 --> 17:18.520
and she is not only a singer. She

17:18.520 --> 17:21.520
has success in the fashion business too.

17:22.600 --> 17:28.620
This starts in 2001. After the success of

17:28.620 --> 17:32.380
The Wedding Planner, Jennifer opens a closed business

17:32.560 --> 17:37.180
with Andy Hilfiger. Andy is the brother of

17:37.180 --> 17:42.020
fashion's famous Tommy Hilfiger. They call their business

17:42.020 --> 17:46.980
Sweetface. There aren't many clothes for big women

17:46.980 --> 17:50.420
but this isn't a problem with Sweetface.

17:51.990 --> 17:57.500
Jennifer starts JLo too. From JLo, women can

17:57.500 --> 18:01.740
buy clothes and perfume too. In a very

18:01.740 --> 18:02.640
short time,

18:02.880 --> 18:07.020
Jennifer's clothes are famous and her perfume Glow

18:07.020 --> 18:08.660
is number one.

18:10.240 --> 18:13.960
But some people are angry about Jennifer's business.

18:15.100 --> 18:18.120
Some of her clothes come from dead animals,

18:18.120 --> 18:24.260
they say. That's not right. Jennifer listens because

18:24.260 --> 18:29.200
she likes animals. Today, those people are happy.

18:30.780 --> 18:34.600
Jennifer is in the food business too. In

18:34.600 --> 18:39.300
April 2002, she opens a place in Pasadena,

18:39.800 --> 18:40.260
California.

18:41.140 --> 18:46.880
Jennifer calls it Madres. Madre is mother in

18:46.880 --> 18:50.740
Spanish. The food there is the Cuban food

18:50.740 --> 18:52.580
of her mother's family.

18:55.790 --> 19:00.260
For the children. Children are important to Jennifer.

19:01.480 --> 19:03.340
She does a lot of charity work

19:03.340 --> 19:06.880
for sick children and she helps families with

19:06.880 --> 19:10.780
very little money. These are important to Mark

19:10.780 --> 19:11.280
too.

19:12.960 --> 19:17.400
Today, Jennifer Lopez and Mark Anthony are famous

19:17.400 --> 19:18.700
for their charity work.

19:20.300 --> 19:24.520
One night in May 2007, the two stars

19:24.520 --> 19:27.520
are in New York with the famous singer

19:27.520 --> 19:28.940
Paul Simon.

19:29.900 --> 19:33.700
They ask people for money for sick children.

19:34.680 --> 19:39.660
The night is a big success. People give

19:39.660 --> 19:41.600
a lot of money to the charity.

19:43.140 --> 19:47.540
And now, Jennifer and Mark have children too.

19:48.800 --> 19:52.520
Jennifer's friends and family are very happy for

19:52.520 --> 19:52.720
them.

19:53.440 --> 19:58.860
For Jennifer, children are very important. This time

19:58.860 --> 20:02.480
is important too. It is a quiet time.

20:03.460 --> 20:11.280
For now, work comes after family. Jennifer Lopez,

20:12.120 --> 20:16.740
the star with many faces. She's a dancer,

20:17.430 --> 20:22.180
a singer, an actress, a business woman, and

20:22.180 --> 20:24.900
she helps unhappy children and families.

20:26.380 --> 20:29.520
Jennifer Lopez does all of these jobs very

20:29.520 --> 20:35.080
well. In the 1990s, Jennifer Lopez was the

20:35.080 --> 20:36.100
number one

20:36.100 --> 20:42.520
actress and dancer in the US. Today, she

20:42.520 --> 20:46.180
is famous for many things in many countries.

20:47.760 --> 20:52.700
From Asia to America, people ask, who is

20:52.700 --> 20:58.400
our number one Latina? The answer is always

20:58.400 --> 20:59.180
the same.

20:59.180 --> 21:02.780
Jennifer Lopez, of course.

